    headline: "Healthcare and agentic AI: HIPAA, FDA SaMD, and the supervision question.",
    dek: "Three regulatory frames a healthcare buyer has to satisfy simultaneously, and the line between platforms that fit administrative use and platforms that require FDA clearance.",
