    headline: "Agentic AI in financial services: FINRA, the SEC, and the audit-trail problem.",
    dek: "Three regulatory regimes converge on one technical question: can the firm reconstruct, on demand, the exact decision sequence an AI agent followed when interacting with a client account? Most platforms cannot. The deals are stalling there.",
    date: "2026-05-09",
